Package org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.application.ambassador.util

Class ClassNameParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.application.ambassador.util.ClassNameParser
  • public class ClassNameParser
extends Object
    This utility class parses a String and awaits at least a class reference. The class reference may be followed by a pair of parenthesis that includes a list of parameters like: com.some.package.name.ClassName(true, 12.45, \"some text\") As a result an instance of the class `ClassName` will be created with the given parameter list.
